description: Footway Group AB engages in the operation of an online shoe retail store. The company is headquartered in Kista, Stockholm and currently employs 48 full-time employees. The company went IPO on 2015-07-13. The firm operates an online shop and offers a wide range of shoes, such as women' shoes, men's shoes and children's shoes. The firm offers a variety of products, such as boots , sandals, slippers, sneakers, sports shoes, warm lined high boots, rubber boots, among others.
name: Footway Group AB
